{"tid":295987,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇住左over廿年既馬鞍山巴絲係度？","createTime":"2017-06-24T08:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T10:59:58.000Z","uid":14779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08db491f38d74497daba868e5948ae68d1e316a2","tid":295987,"uid":14779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T08:17:15.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n細個住過錦英同富寶<br />\n<br />\n呢排四圍兜 兜番上馬鞍山<br />\n<br />\nRecall左好多回憶出黎 包括係以前點樣比呀媽打 利安火燭成家人係度睇 <br />\n<br />\n當中有一件事係好難理解既 唔知有冇其他巴絲有印象<br />\n<br />\n大概係1996-1999年其中一個閒日既日頭<br />\n<br />\n當日唔知打八號波定係紅雨黑雨 係唔洗番學既<br />\n<br />\n當時我就住富寶/錦英 不過多數係富寶 因為係望到錦英路條大斜路 同埋利安個巴士總站既<br />\n<br />\n果陣得我一個係屋企 出面行緊好勁既雷 同埋好大雨<br />\n<br />\n慢慢就變左有警車同救護車既bibu聲 +雨聲行雷聲<br />\n<br />\n咁細個果陣 緊係望出去睇下咩事架啦 <br />\n<br />\n我阿媽間房就對正條大斜路<br />\n<br />\n見有幾架警車打橫擺係錦英路條大斜路 然後有警察向天開槍 又有人大叫<br />\n<br />\n但又唔似槍戰駁火<br />\n<br />\n我既記憶就去到呢度 始終成廿年前<br />\n<br />\n到底有冇咁既事發生過都唔知 定係我細個on99比雷聲嚇親幻想出黎呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有就係我記得以前沙田入馬鞍山唔係行繞道既 同一個位置應該都有條路 果條路好似會經馬鞍山郊野公園下面果條村 依家搵極都搵唔番果條路既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373a894021d5eb368fa6f7bbab2766db69186185","tid":295987,"uid":14779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T08:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4adbfeca7264e488fb02f06e8e843243fa7f2804","tid":295987,"uid":14779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T08:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66d1af35ef5acbbd825b7b0f07abc25c6332808","tid":295987,"uid":14779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T08:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f197aeb0cc6e945673ad326a699096f19be22ee","tid":295987,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T08:59:32.000Z","msg":"30年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7721b45d4718a6b20ab8f9c8cd185de3b8abf65f","tid":295987,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:11:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>30年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1"},{"pid":"22d43e331277d208287dabb194207974488d0d31","tid":295987,"uid":14779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:27:51.000Z","msg":"頭先問左呀媽 佢話係走犯 但係馬鞍山點會走犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4daa2dcfe6d749069631751a5d5776572f67ba36","tid":295987,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:43:33.000Z","msg":"而家沙田入馬鞍山都唔係行繞道<br />\n除非係去烏溪沙或者西沙同西貢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b14c4e3a5602d1cb7448196331e5d20673d13d","tid":295987,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭先問左呀媽 佢話係走犯 但係馬鞍山點會走犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n白石難民"},{"pid":"e86b4ccf627516622935367fcb8959aff28a5e00","tid":295987,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:59:58.000Z","msg":"近幾年太多人喺mos, 每次食飯都要搵位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寧願渣車出去其他地方食<br />\n<br />\n朝早塞車到仆街，比5年前早咗接近30mins出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}